title: kitchen_drawer_flashlight
---
<<if has_flag("paranoid")>>
  <<set_flag "has_flashlight">>
  <<play_sound "flashlightGrab">>
  <<stop>>
<<endif>>
My trusty flashlight.
I probably should get some other tools,
now that I am living alone...
